rows.name:
To think that Chairman Bahn was
involved in illegal business...

rows.label: tlk42400013_04_msg0002
rows.name:
That was truly unexpected,
and shocking, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I had always thought he showed an
unusual attachment to money, but...

rows.label: tlk42400013_04_msg0004
rows.name:
To go that far... I've lost
all respect for him, mo!
